query:
SELECT bd.id, bd.weeklyBonusId, bd.employeeId, bd.weeklyRevenue, bd.bonusAmount, bd.bonusTier, e.name as employeeName 
FROM bonusDetails bd 
LEFT JOIN employees e ON bd.employeeId = e.id 
ORDER BY bd.id DESC LIMIT 10;
